name: AlphabetPosition
0:
”Alexa, open alphabet position”
”Alexa, ask alphabet position to start a game”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: alphabet position
des:
Alexa will tell you a letter. Your job is to tell her the position of the letter in the alphabet. 
Alexa will tell you if you need to guess higher or lower. She will also tell you how many times you have played.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
